data.description: Motivated Seller of this spacious tri level home with a double car garage located in a cul-de-sac. Downstairs bonus room with tile floor leads to large back porch. Kitchen space with open living room. Upstairs you will find three bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. Large master bathroom with double vanities and a tile shower with a stand-alone tub. Renovations in 2017 included a new roof and kitchen cabinets. Located close to shopping, the downtown Fayetteville area, Fort Liberty, and more.
